    &lt;img alt=&#34;Wandering through the garden.&#34; title=&#34;Wandering through the garden.&#34; data-src=&#34;/uploads/2014/5/MtVernon/m/MtVernon_027_m.jpg&#34;&gt;
  &lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;p class=&#39;wp-caption-text&#39;&gt;Wandering through the garden.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;


